rComments: Prof Ye cares about her students and is very approachable. Everything is posted online so lecs and tuts aren't mandatory but the examples done in class help with understanding the material. The wording of questions on evaluations is not always clear, but she is very lenient on part marks. She shares past finals midterms and several helpful examples
